title: Saint Rita Catholic Church: At 100 Years

sources.title: Saint Rita | Full Mini-Series | Beautiful Drama Romance Movie | True Story of Love and Forgiveness
sources.description:
Cascia, 14th century, Rita Liotti falls in love, gets married and has two children. Her dream of love is soon hindered by a masculine and violent society, that Rita faces with peace and forgiveness

2004. Stars: Vittoria Belvedere, Martin Crewes, Simone Ascani
